['DescriptionLime House Real Estate Broker is pleased to offer a beautiful spacious independent villa in Meadows 4:
Property Details:
Ground Floor
- Ground floor has a separate Living, Dinning and a Family room;
- Separate guest room and maids room (both are en-suite);
- 2 covered and dedicated parking;
1st Floor:
- 4 bedrooms and a separate family area;
- Master and second room are en-suite;
  (three-bathrooms upstairs in all)
Special Features:
- Ground floor has a bedroom downstairs with en-suite bathroom;
- Landscaping around the villa;
- Located close to the community centre, petrol pump & private school;
- Easy access to Sheikh Zayed Road;
ORN: 16923, BRN:44412;
Permit Number: 30028;
About Meadows:
The Meadows is an established residential community with an extensive range of lifestyle amenities, which include parks and water features, swimming pools, children’s play area, shopping centres, cafes, and restaurants, and 24-hour security and maintenance. 
For further queries and in arranging viewings, contact +971582161314.']
